{"tid":1794303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連賣演唱會飛系統都攪唔掂既香港政府 話有信心幾日內攪好個全港抽獎系統防炒家黃牛程式 重要可以無限抽到中獎為止喎","createTime":"2019-12-23T04:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T13:32:21.000Z","uid":252492,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"015f6fb2d48ddc755badce0ee392b8108fa4e970","tid":1794303,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"除夕轉玩抽獎送4張任何目的地機票 名額10個料300萬人爭崩頭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191223/60403306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F60403306&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=739b188f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F60403306&h=4b04094d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191223/60403306</a><br />\n<br />\n只要玩一個簡易揭牌遊戲，就有機會得獎，獎品為2萬份總值100元的超市禮券。洪又指，<span style=\"color: green;\">此輪的參加者可無限次參加直至抽得獎品為止，當然，2萬份禮券都送出或當日晚上11時後</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇開始半個鐘就有人寫好bot極速比大陸人d炒家同黃牛程式清哂2萬分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f824a7c0e7764a3d8ff0971dc0349eed4e8b94","tid":1794303,"uid":272603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T04:23:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新德國聯署</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國聯邦議院《全球馬格尼茨基法案》</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">仲差44000人!!!!</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">目標50000人</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"